Comment: Abilities: AEsh (Shadow Strike), Ubertip (Tooltip - Normal - Extended)
Value: Hurls a poisoned dagger at a target enemy unit, dealing <AEsh,DataE1> initial damage, and <AEsh,DataA1> damage every <AEsh,Cast1> seconds for <AEsh,Dur1> seconds. The poison slows the movement speed of the targeted unit by 75% for it's duration.
